Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix:=20full=20audit=20=E2=80=94=20bid=20trackin?=
 =?UTF-8?q?g,=20stellar=20type,=20logging,=20escape=20fixes?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fixes from comprehensive audit of all 105 .py/.yml files:

P1 — Real Bugs:
- src/services/draft_service.py: implement place_bid() auction tracking
  Previously a stub that accepted any bid unconditionally. Now validates
  active nomination, rejects bids ≤ current high, records in
  draft.nomination_bids dict, and logs each bid.
- src/ml/feature_extractor.py: add 'stellar' type to TYPE_IDS (was
  missing while battle_env.py had it at id=19); update /18.0 → /19.0
  normalization to stay consistent with battle_env.

P2 — Code Quality:
- src/ml/feature_extractor.py: fix STATE_FEATURE_DIM comment (was
  showing battle_env 48-dim layout by mistake; actual dim is 19).
- src/ml/train_policy.py: 17x print() → log.info()
- src/ml/train_all.py: 10x print() → log.info()
- src/data/smogon.py: 4x print() → log.warning/info()
- src/ml/replay_parser.py: 1x print() → log.warning()
- src/ml/replay_scraper.py: 2x print() → log.info()

P3 — Minor Warnings:
- tmp/check_obs.py: f-string → rf-string to fix invalid \d escape
- scripts/sync_commands.py: forward slash in docstring usage example
